  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb2 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Angajan Ramanathan's letter to Minister Bandula Gunawardena regarding the distribution of essential food items",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Angajan Ramanathan has submitted a request through a letter to the Minister of Transport and Highways Bandula Gunawardena to arrange alternative routes for the distribution of essential food and medicines between Jaffna and Colombo as requested by the representatives of the Jaffna Chamber of Commerce.",
        "Traders in the Jaffna district have so far used numerous lorries to transport essential food items from Colombo to Jaffna and from Jaffna to Colombo.",
        "Unfortunately, traders in the Jaffna district are unable to use lorries due to the complete cessation of fuel supply under the current economic crisis.",
        "The current crisis situation has worsened and the public has been hit hard by shortages of essential commodities.",
        "Traders in the Jaffna district need about ten or twelve trains for transportation and are willing to pay for it.",
        "Therefore, in view of the urgent need of this issue, I humbly request that the necessary arrangements be made immediately for the transportation of essential items at concessional prices by train."
      ],
